Let's put this around you.

1243
01:32:19.774 --> 01:32:22.610
A little detour. Huh?

1244
01:32:23.512 --> 01:32:24.712
Yeah.

1245
01:32:25.514 --> 01:32:26.881
A little detour.

1246
